        <h3 data-uuid="31fa1e2e429342618f0b21fc7dfc0266">The Impact in Southeast Asia</h3>
        <p data-uuid="fbefc60c61bb4e07b905c8ee23370326">The war ended when North
            Vietnamese forces captured Saigon in April 1975. Communist leaders created the
            Socialist Republic of Vietnam, uniting the former countries of North and South
            Vietnam. Hanoi became the capital, and Saigon was renamed Ho Chi Minh City.</p>
