                <h2 data-uuid="f755687c6f654e01ba09bf6c1c9f0b2b">Causes and Effects of the Vietnam War</h2>
                <p data-uuid="40a58ceb2cbb49739d6cfc8aa62da364">The Vietnam War changed the lives of millions of
                    people, both in Southeast Asia and in the United States. In many ways, the war
                    continues to influence American politics and foreign policy.</p>
            </article>
