        <p data-uuid="886214d88b5f451789efa772ca90a50e">The memorial has become a
            symbol of healing after a long and divisive war. Hundreds of people visit it
            daily. Some visitors leave flowers, personal mementos, or written messages.
            Others simply ponder the meaning of the memorial.</p>
